"唔係講成個chapter，係個chapter其中某一條嘅寫法令到果一條得物無所用<br />\n<br />\n啱規格但lack of maintenance/not proper functioning我估都係屋宇署出repair order<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩個部門各自出site，各有各講，晒錢晒時間晒人力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1c443e22b0a51076b7da4290097055034ff74f","tid":844853,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e6990c47c349c9bde72d366738685ba5f2cf33","tid":844853,"uid":118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e893543a93be0291277a4fae3866aff97735835f","tid":844853,"uid":23786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4239a064f97adc440b6d97762c26606b55fd0ff","tid":844853,"uid":74399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"唔同例唔同講法好正常呀"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"有裝鎖（唔啱規格）但冇鎖就唔關消防事，有裝鎖（唔啱規格）就係咪都關屋宇署事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n消防果條例要嚟做乜，屋宇署做晒得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"因為消防條例寫明大廈嘅逃生出口 防煙門都係不准上鎖<br />\n如果天台同地下上鎖嘅話會喺24小時內巡查執法<br />\n<br />\n所以係無錯喎 同一樣嘢關兩個部門事 大家著眼點唔同啫 都係想為件事好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"消防條例邊度有寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無睇過消防條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通常我見消防剩係理fsi <br />\n即係緊急照明 消防水缸果d<br />\n<br />\n屋宇署就跟建築物條例<br />\n你跟到屋宇署本fire code<br />\n佢就當你comply到條例<br />\n上鎖果d係屋宇署本code有寫"},{"pid":"fc6c93c954abecfe72ae1dcd515356e45cb37434","tid":844853,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e6990c47c349c9bde72d366738685ba5f2cf33","tid":844853,"uid":118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e893543a93be0291277a4fae3866aff97735835f","tid":844853,"uid":23786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4239a064f97adc440b6d97762c26606b55fd0ff","tid":844853,"uid":74399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"唔同例唔同講法好正常呀"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"有裝鎖（唔啱規格）但冇鎖就唔關消防事，有裝鎖（唔啱規格）就係咪都關屋宇署事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n消防果條例要嚟做乜，屋宇署做晒得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"因為消防條例寫明大廈嘅逃生出口 防煙門都係不准上鎖<br />\n如果天台同地下上鎖嘅話會喺24小時內巡查執法<br />\n<br />\n所以係無錯喎 同一樣嘢關兩個部門事 大家著眼點唔同啫 都係想為件事好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:29:51.000Z","msg":"講緊有鎖（唔啱規格）但冇上鎖，消防果條就廢咗，最後都係要用返建築物條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n消防果條唔係講個device本身，而係上鎖果下；而BD係講個device/method of construction<br />\n<br />\n基本上消防果條係真係火燭，個鎖啱規格但又開唔到鎖先有用武之地，到時人都死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFYI:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Cap. 123F</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n41. Means of escape<br />\n<br />\n(1) Every building shall be provided with such means of escape in case of emergency as may be required by the intended use of the building.<br />\n<br />\n(2) Without prejudice to paragraph (1), every building which exceeds 6 storeys in height or in which the level of the floor of the uppermost storey is more than 17 m above the level of the ground at the point of discharge of the main staircase shall, in addition to the main staircase, be provided with a second staircase as means of escape in case of emergency. (L.N. 294 of 1976)<br />\n<br />\n(L.N. 33 of 1966)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Cap. 95F</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n15. Locking of means of escape<br />\n<br />\n(1) A person commits an offence if the person&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n(a) secures or causes to be secured the means of escape in respect of any premises; or<br />\n(b) being the owner, tenant, occupier or person in charge of any premises, permits or suffers to be secured the means of escape in respect of the premises,<br />\n<br />\nby any lock or other device which in the event of fire or other calamity&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n(c) cannot readily and conveniently be opened from within the premises without the use of a key; or<br />\n(d) might render escape materially more difficult."},{"pid":"a221f5e6476a98de21e4936f3bf49cca1c35bf44","tid":844853,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔同例唔同講法好正常呀</blockquote>有裝鎖（唔啱規格）但冇鎖就唔關消防事，有裝鎖（唔啱規格）就係咪都關屋宇署事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n消防果條例要嚟做乜，屋宇署做晒得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>因為消防條例寫明大廈嘅逃生出口 防煙門都係不准上鎖<br />\n如果天台同地下上鎖嘅話會喺24小時內巡查執法<br />\n<br />\n所以係無錯喎 同一樣嘢關兩個部門事 大家著眼點唔同啫 都係想為件事好</blockquote>講緊有鎖（唔啱規格）但冇上鎖，消防果條就廢咗，最後都係要用返建築物條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n消防果條唔係講個device本身，而係上鎖果下；而BD係講個device/method of construction<br />\n<br />\n基本上消防果條係真係火燭又開唔到鎖先有用武之地<span style=\"color: red;\">（唔理個鎖啱唔啱規格）</span>，到時人都死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFYI:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Cap. 123F</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n41. Means of escape<br />\n<br />\n(1) Every building shall be provided with such means of escape in case of emergency as may be required by the intended use of the building.<br />\n<br />\n(2) Without prejudice to paragraph (1), every building which exceeds 6 storeys in height or in which the level of the floor of the uppermost storey is more than 17 m above the level of the ground at the point of discharge of the main staircase shall, in addition to the main staircase, be provided with a second staircase as means of escape in case of emergency. (L.N. 294 of 1976)<br />\n<br />\n(L.N. 33 of 1966)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Cap. 95F</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n15. Locking of means of escape<br />\n<br />\n(1) A person commits an offence if the person&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n(a) secures or causes to be secured the means of escape in respect of any premises; or<br />\n(b) being the owner, tenant, occupier or person in charge of any premises, permits or suffers to be secured the means of escape in respect of the premises,<br />\n<br />\nby any lock or other device which in the event of fire or other calamity&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n(c) cannot readily and conveniently be opened from within the premises without the use of a key; or<br />\n(d) might render escape materially more difficult.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d8048bbc6e877c11a55c66745eba8f1bb8b5fca5","tid":844853,"uid":23786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"btw，個分家就係：<br />\n<br />\n有device裝咗上門就屋宇署，用鎖鏈鎖住就消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9707eaae2b1054e4721d4417f9b16c0e915f9854","tid":844853,"uid":118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8048bbc6e877c11a55c66745eba8