":"咪就係話有鎖但冇鎖到消防都係企喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反BD係睇個device(不論當時有冇鎖上)，假設in case鎖咗係咪readily openable/響鐘自動解鎖"},{"pid":"d931c7f75fe8fafc2fee846d28279c342974e520","tid":844853,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb856aef81cbdd29da4ef7b2ce061a17b4ae1d58","tid":844853,"uid":118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8048bbc6e877c11a55c66745eba8f1bb8b5fca5","tid":844853,"uid":23786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"btw，個分家就係：<br />\n<br />\n有device裝咗上門就屋宇署，用鎖鏈鎖住就消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"應該話有個鎖頭嘅話都關埋BD事 <br />\n如果鎖鏈無扣住就兩個部門唔關事<br />\n<br />\n消防著眼於會唔會影響逃生 例子除咗呢個之外 就係有啲人會喺大廈出入口加裝密碼鎖 而個密碼鎖係奇在大廈入面嘅人要有密碼先出到大廈外 消防都會處理<br />\n<br />\n唔利伸啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"冇fixation/installation一定唔關BD事，因為唔可以當僭建<br />\n<br />\n電閘一定響鐘就斷電啦，唔係就違規構築物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd82331197b96b7a19342db983e39029c8d8e0b","tid":844853,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"其實我係想講，如果1823條友唔識refer去BD同食環，剩係refer去消防，就死得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我一開波已經寫明B(P)R 41，同冇諗過佢會refer去消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2692d54f8ebd88a9eaa3eda8a7f6eaca4ee80361","tid":844853,"uid":148125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"